---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Programmes"
  description="Group, womens, personalised 1-on-1, corporate workshops, kids and security personnel. Practical self defense, rebuilt for the life you actually live."
  activeNav="programmes"
  bodyLabel="04 Programmes">

<!-- PAGE HERO -->
<section class="trainers-hero">
  <div class="trainers-hero-bg">
    <img src="/assets/hero-programmes.jpg" alt="" />
  </div>
  <div class="wrap trainers-hero-overlay">
    <div class="crumb">
      <span>JF SELF DEFENSE</span><span class="sep">/</span><span class="here">PROGRAMMES</span>
    </div>
    <h1 class="display h1 trainers-hero-h1 programmes-hero-h1">
      <span class="prog-hero-l1">Same hierarchy.</span>
      <span class="prog-hero-l2">Rebuilt for <span class="red">your life</span>.</span>
    </h1>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- PROGRAMME LIST -->
<section class="wrap" style="padding-top:0;">
  <div class="prog-page-grid">

    <article class="prog-page" id="women">
      <div class="prog-page-num">01</div>
      <div>
        <h2 class="prog-page-title">Women's self defense</h2>
        <p class="mono" style="color:var(--red);margin-top:10px;">MOST POPULAR · MIXED LEVELS</p>
      </div>
      <p class="prog-page-desc">
        Designed around the situations women actually face: the bus stop after dark,
        the lift home, the persistent stranger, the partner you no longer feel safe
        with. Drills are scenario-led, not technique-led — the question is never "did
        you do it perfectly" but "did you go home safely." Open to all levels; you do
        not need to be fit to start.
      </p>
      <div class="prog-page-meta">
        <span><strong>Format</strong> · weekly group + bookable workshops</span>
        <span><strong>Duration</strong> · 75 min</span>
        <span><strong>From</strong> · S$45 / drop-in</span>
      </div>
      <a class="prog-page-cta" href="#book" data-trial data-trial-programme="Women's self defense">
        Book a trial
        <svg class="arrow" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M5 12h14M13 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
      </a>
    </article>

    <article class="prog-page" id="group">
      <div class="prog-page-num">02</div>
      <div>
        <h2 class="prog-page-title">Group training</h2>
        <p class="mono" style="color:var(--red);margin-top:10px;">WEEKLY · MIXED ADULT</p>
      </div>
      <p class="prog-page-desc">
        The flagship: weekly classes at the Paya Lebar studio. Fitness-led,
        scenario-led, drill-led. You build a working baseline of decisions and
        movement — and over months, that baseline becomes the floor you can think
        from when something happens. Drop-in welcome.
      </p>
      <div class="prog-page-meta">
        <span><strong>Format</strong> · weekly group</span>
        <span><strong>Duration</strong> · 60 min</span>
        <span><strong>From</strong> · S$40 / drop-in</span>
      </div>
      <a class="prog-page-cta" href="#book" data-trial data-trial-programme="Group training">
        Book a trial
        <svg class="arrow" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M5 12h14M13 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
      </a>
    </article>

    <article class="prog-page" id="personal">
      <div class="prog-page-num">03</div>
      <div>
        <h2 class="prog-page-title">Personalised 1-on-1</h2>
        <p class="mono" style="color:var(--red);margin-top:10px;">PRIVATE · BY APPOINTMENT</p>
      </div>
      <p class="prog-page-desc">
        Private sessions with Jeffrey, programmed against the specific risks of your
        routine, commute and travel. The honest option for students who want serious
        progress, or who would rather not train in front of others. Built one
        student at a time.
      </p>
      <div class="prog-page-meta">
        <span><strong>Format</strong> · 1-on-1 with Jeffrey</span>
        <span><strong>Duration</strong> · 60–90 min</span>
        <span><strong>From</strong> · S$180 / session</span>
      </div>
      <a class="prog-page-cta" href="https://wa.me/6596210576?text=Hi%20Jeffrey%2C%20I%27d%20like%20to%20enquire%20about%20Personalised%201-on-1%20training." target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        Contact Jeffrey
        <svg class="arrow" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M5 12h14M13 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
      </a>
    </article>

    <article class="prog-page" id="corporate">
      <div class="prog-page-num">04</div>
      <div>
        <h2 class="prog-page-title">Corporate workshops</h2>
        <p class="mono" style="color:var(--red);margin-top:10px;">ON-SITE · HALF / FULL-DAY</p>
      </div>
      <p class="prog-page-desc">
        Half-day and full-day sessions delivered on-site for teams of 12–40. Trusted
        by SUSS, Celanese, Sloane Clinic, National Healthcare Group, Emerson and
        Latham &amp; Watkins. A practical wellbeing offer that actually makes a
        difference — and a memorable team day, not another e-learning module.
      </p>
      <div class="prog-page-meta">
        <span><strong>Format</strong> · on-site at your office</span>
        <span><strong>Duration</strong> · 3 or 6 hours</span>
        <span><strong>From</strong> · S$2,400 / half-day · POA</span>
      </div>
      <a class="prog-page-cta" href="#book" data-trial data-trial-programme="Corporate workshop">
        Request a proposal
        <svg class="arrow" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M5 12h14M13 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
      </a>
    </article>

    <article class="prog-page" id="kids">
      <div class="prog-page-num">05</div>
      <div>
        <h2 class="prog-page-title">Kids &amp; families</h2>
        <p class="mono" style="color:var(--red);margin-top:10px;">AGES 7–14 · WEEKEND</p>
      </div>
      <p class="prog-page-desc">
        Confidence, boundaries, situational awareness — taught to children in
        language they already understand. No tournaments, no belts, no fear. The
        curriculum is designed alongside parents and educators, and aimed squarely at
        the bullying and stranger-risk situations real Singapore kids encounter.
      </p>
      <div class="prog-page-meta">
        <span><strong>Format</strong> · weekend group</span>
        <span><strong>Duration</strong> · 45 min</span>
        <span><strong>From</strong> · S$35 / drop-in</span>
      </div>
      <a class="prog-page-cta" href="#book" data-trial data-trial-programme="Kids &amp; families">
        Book a trial
        <svg class="arrow" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M5 12h14M13 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
      </a>
    </article>

    <article class="prog-page" id="security">
      <div class="prog-page-num">06</div>
      <div>
        <h2 class="prog-page-title">Security personnel</h2>
        <p class="mono" style="color:var(--red);margin-top:10px;">PROFESSIONAL · BY APPLICATION</p>
      </div>
      <p class="prog-page-desc">
        Specialised training for working officers, protective staff, and corporate
        security teams. Drawn from three decades on the other side of the badge.
        Curriculum scoped per engagement; references available on application.
      </p>
      <div class="prog-page-meta">
        <span><strong>Format</strong> · bespoke programme</span>
        <span><strong>Duration</strong> · varies</span>
        <span><strong>Cost</strong> · POA</span>
      </div>
      <a class="prog-page-cta" href="#book" data-trial data-trial-programme="Security personnel">
        Apply now
        <svg class="arrow" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M5 12h14M13 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
      </a>
    </article>

  </div>
</section>

<!-- PACKAGES -->
<section class="section section-tight">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-head">
      <div><span class="section-head-num">PACKAGES</span></div>
      <div>
        <h2 class="display h2 section-head-title">
          Train at the pace<br/>that suits your life.
        </h2>
        <p class="lede" style="margin-top:20px;">
          Packages apply to group, women's and 1-on-1 programmes. Sessions are valid
          for twelve months from purchase and transferable across formats.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="pkg-grid">
      <div class="pkg">
        <span class="pkg-h">STARTER</span>
        <div class="pkg-n">4<span class="x"> sessions</span></div>
        <p class="pkg-d">Four sessions, ~5% off drop-in. Best for trying the school out before committing.</p>
        <a class="prog-page-cta" href="#book" data-trial data-trial-programme="Group training">Get started
          <svg class="arrow" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M5 12h14M13 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="pkg featured">
        <span class="pkg-h">MOST POPULAR</span>
        <div class="pkg-n">8<span class="x"> sessions</span></div>
        <p class="pkg-d">Eight sessions, ~12% off drop-in. The sweet spot for building working memory and movement habits.</p>
        <a class="prog-page-cta" href="#book" data-trial data-trial-programme="Group training">Get started
          <svg class="arrow" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M5 12h14M13 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="pkg">
        <span class="pkg-h">SERIOUS</span>
        <div class="pkg-n">12<span class="x"> sessions</span></div>
        <p class="pkg-d">Twelve sessions, ~18% off drop-in. For students who plan to make this part of the year.</p>
        <a class="prog-page-cta" href="#book" data-trial data-trial-programme="Group training">Get started
          <svg class="arrow" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M5 12h14M13 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="small" style="margin-top:20px;">Indicative pricing for mockup. Final rates to be confirmed with Jeffrey.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- FAQ-ish belt -->
<section class="section-tight" style="border-top:1px solid var(--line);padding:64px 0;">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="faq-belt">
      <div>
        <div class="foot-h">First class?</div>
        <p class="body" style="font-size:15px;">
          Wear comfortable workout gear. We train barefoot or in clean indoor shoes.
          Bring water. No experience needed — most of our students started knowing
          nothing.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="foot-h">Will I get hurt?</div>
        <p class="body" style="font-size:15px;">
          Classes are designed to be scalable and safe. We use protective equipment
          for any contact work, and Jeffrey programmes based on the body in front of
          him. Bruises happen. Injuries are rare.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="foot-h">What if I can't make it weekly?</div>
        <p class="body" style="font-size:15px;">
          Packages are valid twelve months. Many of our working-parent students train
          every other week and still build real capability over a year. Show up when
          you can.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CONTACT — inline form, page-bottom -->
<section class="contact-section" id="book">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="contact-inner">
      <div class="contact-pitch">
        <span class="eyebrow"><span class="dot"></span>BOOK A TRIAL</span>
        <h2>
          Pick a programme.<br/>Send a short note.<br/>
          <span class="red">We'll take it from there.</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="body" style="font-size:16px;max-width:42ch;">
          Trial sessions for women's &amp; group are S$45. Personal training trials
          are S$180. Corporate proposals and security-personnel applications are
          quoted per engagement.
        </p>
        <div class="contact-side">
          <div class="contact-side-row">
            <span class="label">STUDIO</span>
            <span class="val">414 Upper Paya Lebar Road, L2 Prestige Point<br/>Singapore 534994</span>
          </div>
          <div class="contact-side-row">
            <span class="label">EMAIL</span>
            <span class="val"><a href="mailto:Jeffrey.f@jfselfdefense.com">Jeffrey.f@jfselfdefense.com</a></span>
          </div>
          <div class="contact-side-row">
            <span class="label">WHATSAPP</span>
            <span class="val"><a href="https://wa.me/6596210576" target="_blank" rel="noopener">+65 9621 0576</a></span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div data-inline-trial-form></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- FOOTER -->

</BaseLayout>
